"Going to Costa Rica is a dream come true"
In an exclusive interview with Viva, Pearl Jam bassist Jeff Ament said the band is ready to perform one of their best concerts next Sunday at the National Stadium.
It has been more than 20 years of waiting, but the band claims that for them it will also make the dream of playing in the country a reality.
